\section{Introduction}

A nonincreasing sequence of positive integers $(\lambda = (\lambda_1, \lambda_2, \dots , \lambda_i)$ such that $\sum \lambda_j = n$ is a partition of $n$, denoted $\lambda \vdash n$.  We say that $n$ is the weight of the partition, or write $\vert \lambda \vert = n$.  Denote the number of partitions of $n$ by $p(n)$.  Their generating function is

